snippet.title: NEON INFERNO: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2957720/Neon_Inferno/

NYC 2055: a city beyond salvation. Blast your way through this dense urban jungle in NEON INFERNO, an exciting blend of 2D run-and-gun and gallery-shooter, and help the Family dominate its streets!

Official website (including presskit): https://neoninferno.com
